nekromantik ( also known as &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1987 german horror film directed by werner herzog . the film is a sequel to the 1987 film nekromantik . the film was released in the united states as the title character . the film was a critical and commercial failure . the film was seized and confiscated in the uk under section 3 of the obscene publications act 1959 in the united states .